<h1 id="cc-title" class="text-center">Cleric</h1>

<h2 id="cc-subtitle" class="text-center mb-5">Emotion Domain</h2>

<p id="subclass-overview-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5 p-2 rounded"><i>The Emotion Domain focuses on the core of what
    makes every living creature unique: the various emotions they experienced. Collectively known as the Prismatic
    Pantheon, the Emotional Beings each govern one of the seven primary emotions of the emotional spectrum. While each
    have different views on matters and promote a variety of values to be treasured by their worshipers, clerics of the
    Emotion Domain are conduits that channels the very essence of their Being and guide others that following one's
    heart is not foolish but freeing.</i></p>

