<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Bonus Proficiency</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3">You gain proficiency in Insight.</p>

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Heed My Words</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3">Twice per long rest, you can cast the Command spell without expending
  a spell slot and as a bonus action.</p>

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Channel Divinity: Command Behavior</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5">At 2nd level, as an action, choose a creature that you can see. That
  creature must make a Wisdom saving throw. If fail, you may make the target feel a certain emotion towards a certain
  creature. The target becomes charmed by, frightened of or hostiles towards the creature of your choice that you can
  see. This effect lasts for 1 minute.</p>

