<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Spectrum's Chosen</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5">Beginning at 8th level, all damage spells you cast now do an additional
  1d8 + your Wisdom modifier Psychic damage. In addition, you are immune to all emotion-based effects that would affect
  you negatively.</p>

<hr class="mx-5 mb-5">

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Prismatic Herald</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5">At 17th level, once per long rest, you can choose to drop to 1 hit
  point instead when you would be reduced to 0 hit points. In addition, if you or an ally within 30 ft of you roll a
  natural 20 on a saving throw, you regain a use of your Channel Divinity.</p>